{"title":"倪萍的生长计划","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4070","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>众所周知，伟大的809班班长倪萍，身高不足150cm，作为学霸的她，忍不住同学们的冷嘲热讽，于是她励志打增高针。每个增高针价值各不相同，效果也各不相同。但是倪萍的个人财产有限，作为她的老公的朋友（就是小编啦），必须帮帮朋友的老婆。假设倪萍身高初始有150cm，求最大能长到多高。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个数，N，M表示，有N个增高针，倪萍有M元钱</p><p>后面N行 每行两个整数，表示增高针的价格，与效果。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出一个整数，保证&lt;=maxlongint，表示倪萍最多可以长到多高。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3 70</p><p><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\">100 71\n1 69\n2 1</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>220</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>30%数据 小于等于20</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}